contentrichtext.text: '''YTV''' or '''ytv''' may refer to: * [[YTV (TV channel)]], a Canadian youth television station owned by Corus Entertainment * [[Helsinki Metropolitan Area Council]], a co-operation agency operating in the Helsinki Metropolitan Area * [[KYTV (TV)]], an NBC affiliated television station in Springfield, Missouri * [[Yorkshire Television]], part of the ITV network in the United Kingdom * [[Yomiuri Telecasting Corporation]], a TV station joining Nippon News Network and Nippon Television Network System in Osaka, Japan * [[WYTV]], an ABC affiliated television station in Youngstown, Ohio * [[WHYY-TV]], a PBS member station in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania {{disambiguation}}
